This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with face age progression and image generation using generative adversarial networks. The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which makes it likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories.
